Alaska Silence &amp; Solitude
Alaska Silence &amp; Solitude is the follow up to Alone in the Wilderness, filmed 20
years later. Bob Swerer and Bob Swerer Sr. visit Dick Proenneke at his famous
cabin on Twin Lakes where the wildlife is still abundant and the scenery is
spectacular.

